</P>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Just before 11 a.m. EDT, the Dow industrials  
were up 29.45 points at 11,177.55. Advancing issues on the New York 
Stock Exchange led decliners 1,500-904. The Nasdaq was up 3.77 at 
2,821.90. 

