<HEADLINE> Cullen To Remain Lightning Assistant </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	TAMPA, Fla. (AP) -- John Cullen will be retained as an assistant  
coach with the Tampa Bay Lightning for next season, however Rick 
Paterson and Paulin Bordeleau will be assigned to other positions 
in the organization. 
</P>
