they expected the roof to remain open for the evening, despite a 
chance of rain. 
</P>
<P>
	The last time a baseball game in Seattle was played outside a  
dome was in 1969, when the Pilots played at Sick's Stadium. After 
one season, the expansion team moved to Milwaukee and became the 
