</P>
<P>
	Both are eligible for free agency after the 2000 season, and it  
may cost $400 million or more to keep them. Rodriguez's agent, 
Scott Boras, is expected to seek a 10-year deal averaging $20 
million per season or more. 
</P>
<P>
	Fans, who angst daily about the future of their superstars, set  
aside their worries for the night. They cheered as the roof opened 
to the score from the movie ``2001: A Space Odyssey,'' performed by 
The Seattle Symphony Orchestra on the other side of the 
center-field wall. 
</P>
